kind decision
title Hooks must clear git-local env before nested git tests
status active
edge applies-to blob:a8d371695ff7e4a4fb1b52bf071cfde9d1c45c78
edge targets-path path:hooks/pre-commit

Git hooks inherit repo-local environment variables like GIT_DIR and GIT_WORK_TREE. If the pre-commit hook launches the test suite without clearing them, the inner temporary repos in test/test.sh can accidentally target the outer checkout.

Use `git rev-parse --local-env-vars` and unset those vars before running nested git-based tests from hooks.
